Titolo: Dragonseeds

Anno: 1998

Descrizione: Dragonseeds, released in Japan as Dragon Seeds: Saishū Shinka Keitai (ドラゴンシーズ ～最終進化形態～, Doragon Shīzu ～Saishū Shinka Keitai～, lit. "Dragon Seeds: Final Evolution Form"), is a video game where the player must clone a dragon and train it to fight. The player gets to choose from five basic dragon types and two secret dragons. The game also allows the player to receive extra dragons through the saves files of certain games, if the memory card is placed at the second slot. The game also allows a two-player mode, where each player can battle each other with their own dragons.